pageContext.claim: “Plus, we had tremendous success with governors. I mean, you look at Ohio. You look at Florida. You look at Georgia. I mean, Georgia, as you know, President Obama was there; Michelle was there; Oprah was there. And I was there all by myself. And, in all fairness, Mike went also about four times.”
pageContext.analysis: Michelle Obama did not visit Georgia or campaign for Democratic governor candidate Stacey Abrams.
